  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can also be played solo! Create your own original burger!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378280/extras/773c4f99405045960494485156a4828f.avif?t=1768050078\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378280/extras_big/773c4f99405045960494485156a4828f.avif?t=1768050078 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also use a knife to cut authentic patties, tomatoes, and other ingredients.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378280/extras/00c93d3c805e1ada8baa1ca470b9fd44.avif?t=1768050078\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378280/extras_big/00c93d3c805e1ada8baa1ca470b9fd44.avif?t=1768050078 width=800 height=464 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The in-store computer handles various tasks, such as purchasing ingredients, changing the delivery bike's license plate, and changing the color of the store's floor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378280/extras/a64f55c0758cc6d5f6e2c8850c56bb93.avif?t=1768050078\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378280/extras_big/a64f55c0758cc6d5f6e2c8850c56bb93.avif?t=1768050078 width=800 height=486 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can even ride a bike and ride around town! Have your own elegant journey!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378280/extras/26da7a071807d2772c8b1c7e1d2135e3.avif?t=1768050078\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378280/extras_big/26da7a071807d2772c8b1c7e1d2135e3.avif?t=1768050078 width=800 height=488 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make burgers efficiently and have your own competition!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can also be played solo! Create your own original burger!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378280/extras/773c4f99405045960494485156a4828f.avif?t=1768050078\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378280/extras_big/773c4f99405045960494485156a4828f.avif?t=1768050078 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also use a knife to cut authentic patties, tomatoes, and other ingredients.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378280/extras/00c93d3c805e1ada8baa1ca470b9fd44.avif?t=1768050078\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378280/extras_big/00c93d3c805e1ada8baa1ca470b9fd44.avif?t=1768050078 width=800 height=464 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The in-store computer handles various tasks, such as purchasing ingredients, changing the delivery bike's license plate, and changing the color of the store's floor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378280/extras/a64f55c0758cc6d5f6e2c8850c56bb93.avif?t=1768050078\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378280/extras_big/a64f55c0758cc6d5f6e2c8850c56bb93.avif?t=1768050078 width=800 height=486 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can even ride a bike and ride around town! Have your own elegant journey!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378280/extras/26da7a071807d2772c8b1c7e1d2135e3.avif?t=1768050078\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378280/extras_big/26da7a071807d2772c8b1c7e1d2135e3.avif?t=1768050078 width=800 height=488 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make burgers efficiently and have your own competition!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
